			<h1>Welcome to the NDEx Prototype Site</h1>

				<p>This site provides a preview of the functionality of NDEx, the Network Data Exchange</p>

				<p>NDEx will be an open-source, web-based software system to enable individuals, groups, and 
				software applications to share, store, manipulate, and publish biological network knowledge. </p>


				<p>NDEx is a project of the <a href="http://www.cytoscape.org" target="_blank">Cytoscape Constortium </a> in conjunction with the <a href="http://www.idekerlab.ucsd.edu" target="_blank">Ideker Lab at the UCSD School of Medicine.</a></p>

				<p>Learn more about NDEx at the <a href="http://ndexbio.org" target="_blank">NDEx Project Site.</a></p>

				<p>Techincal details for NDEx are documented at the <a href="http://www.github.com/cytoscape/NDEx-Site/wiki" target="_blank">NDEx Github Repository Wiki.</a>

